metadata.name: Prologue: The Fins That Were Danced to Existence
metadata.description:
Once upon a time, there was a place where living beings existed. 

All beings in that place looked different in color. They had different personalities and motives, although they started existing in the same place, in the same way.

Yet they managed to embrace one another as they were. No discrimination or marginalization happened there.

And they danced happily ever after.
